<D>__{let me do this. i won't make you look bad.}
<A>__{beat.}
<C>__{lobruto}
<D>__{no. you won't. that's what i need to make sure you understand. i remove you now: i'm covered, i took some action.}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{if you go on with this, when you lose blame has to come down. and it'll come down on you. i will have to investigate you for improprieties, incompetence anything i can. in public. i will hang you out to dry. for the good of this office.}
